+  /// Provides facilities to print informations about types into a stream in a user friendly formatting.
+  /// It also supports indentation.
+  /// This class is movable but not copyable, thus not regular.
+  ///
+  /// Example:
+  /// ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~/
+  ///
